---
import Cover from "../assets/images/image-web-3-desktop.jpg";
---

<section class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
  <div class="row mb-3">
    <img src={Cover} alt="cover image" class="img-fluid" />
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
      <h1 class="title">
        The Bright <br /> Future of Web <br class="d-md-none d-xl-block" /> 3.0?
      </h1>
    </div>
    <main class="col-12 col-md-6 h-100 d-md-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
      <p class="text-muted">
        We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to put the power
        of the platforms back into the hands of the people. But is it really
        fulfilling its promise?
      </p>
      <div>
        <button class="custom-btn">READ MORE</button>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</section>
